1
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:29,820
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,820 --> 00:00:31,937
=Episode 14=
(I want to be your little dog,)

3
00:00:32,025 --> 00:00:34,725
(kissing you 3,500 times every day.)

4
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:37,480
Bai!

5
00:00:37,520 --> 00:00:38,360
Zhao!

6
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:40,480
Hua, Bai!

7
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:41,440
Zhao!

8
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:53,280
Zhao, are you alright?

9
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:54,880
(Xi is a good demon.)

10
00:00:54,880 --> 00:00:56,280
(If you dare touch her again,)

11
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:57,920
(even if you are Heaven itself,)

12
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,440
(I will fight you to the end.)

13
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:01,800
(Whether she is human or demon,)

14
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:03,440
(I need not kill her.)

15
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:05,440
(Love between gods and demons)

16
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,800
(is forbidden by the universe.)

17
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:09,120
(If you insist on loving her,)

18
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:11,120
(I will kill her,)

19
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:13,160
(and then destroy you.)

20
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,000
Boss, don't be afraid.

21
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,760
It's just a falling star.

22
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:20,080
Where did you go?

23
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:21,960
Weren't you guarding outside?

24
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:22,760
I...

25
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,800
Xi!

26
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:25,400
(Baihua Hall)
Xi!

27
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,320
- Chief Zhang?
- My lady!

28
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:28,760
Chief Zhang called us early this morning

29
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,040
and said he had something for you.

30
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:32,160
I'm glad you came,
but you didn't have to bring all this.

31
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:33,880
Cut the formalities!

32
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,440
Xi, did you forget?

33
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:38,320
It's your birthday today.

34
00:01:41,400 --> 00:01:43,520
I'm already this old.
I stopped celebrating long ago.

35
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,440
How can that be?

36
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:46,240
I even prepared a gift for you.

37
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:55,960
I have long admired you.

38
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,160
I'd like to stay beside you
as your partner.

39
00:01:58,960 --> 00:01:59,760
These past days,

40
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,240
I've come to realize something.

41
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:03,240
I don't want to see you
being bullied anymore.

42
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,760
If we get married,

43
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,760
I'll have the right
to protect you properly.

44
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:09,760
Today, I sincerely ask again,

45
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,800
please marry me.

46
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:26,320
(If you insist on loving her,)

47
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:28,320
(I will kill her.)

48
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:32,040
(If I leave Xi,)

49
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:33,880
(Heaven won't harm her.)

50
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,520
(Maybe...)

51
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,825
(Baihua Hall)

52
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,400
My lady.

53
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,400
Chief Zhang carries himself well

54
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,040
and is well-educated.

55
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:48,400
He has stayed by your side for years.

56
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,400
He can surely give you happiness.

57
00:03:02,562 --> 00:03:04,262
(Baihua Hall)

58
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,120
Chief Zhang,

59
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,800
you're a good man.

60
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,480
I've always seen you as a brother.

61
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,480
Xi, I know

62
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:25,400
you're still upset about what happened

63
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,720
with that butcher.

64
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:29,520
I failed to protect you then.

65
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,400
- Chief Zhang.
- I...

66
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,800
Let's just stick to being best buds,
like we've always been.

67
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,520
It's getting late,

68
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,800
so I won't keep you for dinner.

69
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,840
It really

70
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,120
is late.

71
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:53,800
You should head back.

72
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,240
Hua, Bai,

73
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,640
let's go inside.

74
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,080
We'll go in first.

75
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:40,240
My lady,

76
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:41,680
stop drinking.

77
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:42,920
Where's Zhao?

78
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,960
No idea.

79
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:46,280
After Chief Zhang left,
he disappeared too.

80
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,360
I'm so mad!

81
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:54,250
If you've got any sense,
get back here now!

82
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:57,600
My lady, don't be sad.

83
00:04:57,920 --> 00:05:00,240
There are countless men in the world.

84
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,520
If he left, then let him go.

85
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,600
But,

86
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:10,160
there's only one him.

87
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:13,360
And there's only one you too, My lady.

88
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:20,280
I measured him,

89
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,800
pretended to limp for him,

90
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,280
and he pushed me to someone else.

91
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:26,520
That blockhead.

92
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,800
Today is my birthday,

93
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:31,480
and he didn't even
wish me "happy birthday".

94
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:33,520
And

95
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:35,360
he even told me

96
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:38,840
"I'll always be here from now on".
What nonsense!

97
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,920
As expected,

98
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,480
men are all talk.

99
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:46,360
It's only been a few days
and he's already gone.

100
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:48,600
Stop crying.

101
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:49,920
Fine.

102
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:54,160
Ye Zhao,

103
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,720
I don't want you anymore.

104
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:58,160
Goodbye, Ye Zhao.

105
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,800
But I don't want to say goodbye.

106
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,600
We're so sleepy.

107
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,160
We're going to bed.

108
00:06:58,600 --> 00:06:59,600
I... I...

109
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,150
I don't want to.

110
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,360
Zhao!

111
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:04,680
I haven't eaten yet!

112
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,840
Why did you drag me here?

113
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:20,400
I haven't eaten yet.

114
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,520
So dramatic.

115
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,160
Don't disturb them.

116
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:26,040
This is better than any storybook.

117
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,160
Boss,

118
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:30,960
I'm leaving.

119
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:32,360
Zhao.

120
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,480
Do you love me?

121
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,840
I said,

122
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,720
I'm leaving.

123
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:50,680
I'll walk you out.

124
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,720
No need.

125
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,600
We won't

126
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,160
meet again.

127
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,920
I said,

128
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,600
I'll walk you out.

129
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:22,160
He Xi, you're overthinking.

130
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:25,040
A divine heart can't give rise to love.

131
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:27,160
How could it love a demon?

132
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:30,360
Forget me.

133
00:08:32,480 --> 00:08:33,800
Pretend I was never here.

134
00:08:36,160 --> 00:08:37,360
What did you say?

135
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,600
I don't care

136
00:08:40,040 --> 00:08:41,720
why you're leaving suddenly.

137
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:44,920
Under that night sky,

138
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,120
I heard

139
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,360
your heart clearly.

140
00:08:51,800 --> 00:08:53,400
If you let me go now,

141
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,600
you won't be able to hold me again.

142
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:00,120
I'll hold someone else's hand,

143
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,600
kiss someone else,

144
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,920
and marry someone else.

145
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,160
Will that not matter to you?

146
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:54,000
♪When starlight cuts
through the long night♪

147
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,560
I was too hesitant

148
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:56,760
and indecisive.

149
00:09:56,875 --> 00:09:59,712
♪It bids farewell to another blue sky♪

150
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,960
But love is love.

151
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:04,360
To hell with those heavenly rules!

152
00:10:04,537 --> 00:10:06,337
♪To see is to part again♪

153
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,840
I just want us

154
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,360
to be together.

155
00:10:12,962 --> 00:10:16,900
♪Unwilling to stop♪

156
00:10:18,212 --> 00:10:23,300
♪As raindrops kiss the ground♪

157
00:10:25,387 --> 00:10:30,437
♪Soaking these hazy, drowsy eyes♪

158
00:10:31,937 --> 00:10:34,187
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

159
00:10:34,240 --> 00:10:35,720
From this day on,

160
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,720
all my remaining days

161
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,040
belong to you.

162
00:10:45,612 --> 00:10:50,362
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

163
00:10:50,412 --> 00:10:53,150
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

164
00:10:53,150 --> 00:11:00,200
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

165
00:11:00,312 --> 00:11:04,687
♪Let the long shadows♪

166
00:11:04,775 --> 00:11:07,537
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

167
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:14,725
♪If in a dream♪

168
00:11:30,237 --> 00:11:31,997
♪I can hear your voice♪

169
00:11:31,997 --> 00:11:34,327
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

170
00:11:34,867 --> 00:11:37,287
♪Let it be us♪

171
00:11:37,587 --> 00:11:39,237
♪drawing endlessly close♪

172
00:11:39,237 --> 00:11:44,667
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

173
00:11:44,897 --> 00:11:46,437
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

174
00:11:46,437 --> 00:11:49,187
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

175
00:11:49,187 --> 00:11:52,157
♪Not even in time♪

176
00:11:52,157 --> 00:11:54,707
♪to tell you how I feel♪

177
00:11:54,707 --> 00:11:59,037
♪If the rain won't stop♪

178
00:11:59,347 --> 00:12:01,797
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

179
00:12:01,957 --> 00:12:08,747
♪Let love go on♪
